title: 865. Falcons Run Game & Are the Eagles a Legit Super Bowl Contender?
itunes:title: 865. Falcons Run Game & Are the Eagles a Legit Super Bowl Contender?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys discuss if the Eagles are a legit Super Bowl contender and also look at how they built their team. Next, the pair look at a team that's doing something unique, the Atlanta Falcons. To wrap up the show, the duo break down the Broncos slow start on offense this season.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
